{"tid":1804311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荔枝角政府合署疑遭火魔法","createTime":"2019-12-31T01:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T09:31:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":527,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":125,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab02db92be42f15cc7acd6e5679be46b9d8a034","tid":1804311,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:51:21.000Z","msg":"今日（31日）凌晨四時許，警方接報指荔枝角政府合署，有人淋潑不明液體及投擲懷疑汽油彈，上址保安遂向警方報案。現場可見，荔枝角政府合署門外有熏黑痕跡遺下。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，發現上址捲閘被熏黑，經初步調查，相信起火原因有可疑，警員並在現場檢獲一些玻璃碎片，以及裝有不明液體的膠樽及玻璃樽作檢驗。警方將案件列縱火，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第六隊跟進，暫未有人被捕，火警中無人受傷，毋須疏散。警方現正追緝約六名疑人，案發時身穿黑色衣物及戴黑色頭套。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3781989/org/0a33b0b9733e0f4d6b41fc0a110556f6.jpg/PthIBz46p1cb-uLvihyuoVpyJfbePGuNNn9fJTZ_XyU?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3781989%2Forg%2F0a33b0b9733e0f4d6b41fc0a110556f6.jpg%2FPthIBz46p1cb-uLvihyuoVpyJfbePGuNNn9fJTZ_XyU%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=5b0d3071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，近期多個政府設施被掟汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n本月26日，凌晨一時許上水警署被發現燒焦痕跡，外牆有燒焦痕迹，據報地面遺有玻璃碎片，疑遭人掟汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n本月22日，牛頭角警署被擲汽油彈，大閘及外牆同熏黑。<br />\n<br />\n本月8日，民陣舉行遊行，高等法院及終審法院先後遭縱火懷疑遭人投擲汽油彈後。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/415837/%E8%8D%94%E6%9E%9D%E8%A7%92%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%90%88%E7%BD%B2%E7%96%91%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%9F%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8D%B2%E9%96%98%E7%86%8F%E9%BB%91-%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2%E9%81%BA%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f6c49895e4f1b8e5a21afe352d3454fe3f3c7099","tid":1804311,"uid":223407,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2uEFoz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2uEFoz8.jpg&h=3da9b664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國聯署<br />\n1. deadline 25/12 (成功) <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=3c40e559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a><br />\n2. deadline 30/12 (成功) <a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=67b6b518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a><br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">deadline  1 月 1 號</span></span> 仲要26,000人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚴重唔夠簽名</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a><br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=12c62134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n簽完share條link去tg"},{"pid":"1e850347d0819452e57e9e93f337c0015b9e1dd1","tid":1804311,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T01:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59a6fbda6c9c19c3001f7144d7a8